item.title: CVE-2023-22322|2024-08-02T10:07:05.987Z -- omron%20corporation -- cx-motion%20pro
item.description: Improper restriction of XML external entity reference (XXE) vulnerability exists in OMRON CX-Motion Pro 1.4.6.013 and earlier. If a user opens a specially crafted project file created by an attacker, sensitive information in the file system where CX-Motion Pro is installed may be disclosed.
